RESIDENTIAL LEASE AGREEMENT

Landlord:
Ridgeview Properties LLC

Tenant:
Bhaskar

1. Term. The lease term shall begin on August 1, 2026 and continue on a month-to-month basis, automatically renewing unless terminated by either party with 30 days' written notice.

2. Security Deposit. Tenant shall pay a security deposit equal to one month rent, payable in the amount of $2,000 upon signing, refundable subject to the condition of the premises at move-out.

3. Rent. The monthly rent thereafter shall be $1,500, due on the 1st of each month.

4. Late Fee. A late fee of 8% of the monthly rent will be charged for any payment received after the 5th of the month.

5. Entry. Landlord may enter the premises for inspection or repairs with 12 hours notice to the Tenant.
